caption: I absolutely loved this wonderful restaurant's pizza and service. Their pepperoni pizza had lots of flavor and their chicken parmigiana pizza was great as well. My favorite part, though was the crust. Usually I find crust is just alright, not really worthy of much notice,  but it was the complete opposite with this pizza. The crust was light, airy, not to crispy and not too soft. It was just right. Their chicken parmigian crust was even better. Phenomenal. It was flaky and every bite of that crust was a pleasure. I would buy just the crust because it was so good. The staff were very generous and kind. They handled an unhappy customer wonderfully, though I dont agree with that customer's judgement. I came around Easter so I was gifted with zeppolis. They look and taste delicious. They also provided me with a pizza cutter which I think was extremely generous. I would come back here anytime. Thank you for showing gratitude and making great food.
